e.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Keith_Griner_Buda_Mendes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Keith_Griner_Buda_Mendes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zach-bryan">扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan)</a>宣布明年夏天将在美国举办三场大型演出，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">莱昂国王 (Kings Of Leon)</a>也将加入其中。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="678" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-3753952"><b>莱昂之王如何重拾自信：“我们还没有准备好放弃”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位乡村明星将于 2025 年 7 月 18 日、19 日和 20 日在距离纽约市仅数英里的新泽西州东卢瑟福的大都会人寿体育场 (MetLife Stadium) 上演头条新闻，由于需求旺盛，前两场演出将被添加。</p><p> <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fzach-bryan-tickets%2Fartist%2F2811359" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在</a>纽约巨人队和纽约喷气机队的主场大型户外体育场查找剩余的演出门票。</p><p>布莱恩在 Instagram 上发布了有关演出的信息：“在大都会人寿体育场比赛一直是我的梦想，所以我们和莱昂国王队一起实现这一目标。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCU-CHpPQis/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: